"title": "4554: yeast",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "4554",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>A raising agent commonly used in bread. Bread that was required quickly was baked without yeast, as at the first Passover, commemorated annually in the Feast of Unleavened Bread. Although some non-meat offerings contained yeast, it could not be burned on the altar.</p>\n<h2>Unleavened bread was made without yeast</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod12:39\">EXO 12:39</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen19:3\">GEN 19:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod12:8-Exod12:11\">EXO 12:8–12:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod12:34\">EXO 12:34</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg6:17-Judg6:19\">JDG 6:17–6:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam28:24-1Sam28:25\">1SA 28:24–28:25</a></p>\n<h2>The consumption of yeast was prohibited during the Feast of Unleavened Bread</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod12:14-Exod12:15\">EXO 12:14–12:15</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod12:17-Exod12:20\">EXO 12:17–12:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod13:3\">EXO 13:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod13:6-Exod13:7\">EXO 13:6–13:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod23:15\">EXO 23:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod23:18\">EXO 23:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod34:18\">EXO 34:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev23:6\">LEV 23:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num28:17\">NUM 28:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut16:1-Deut16:4\">DEU 16:1–16:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek45:21\">EZK 45:21</a></p>\n<h2>Sacrifices burned on the altar were not to contain yeast</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev2:11\">LEV 2:11</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod29:1-Exod29:3\">EXO 29:1–29:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod29:22-Exod29:24\">EXO 29:22–29:24</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod34:25\">EXO 34:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev2:4-Lev2:5\">LEV 2:4–2:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev6:16-Lev6:17\">LEV 6:16–6:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev7:12-Lev7:13\">LEV 7:12–7:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev8:2-Lev8:3\">LEV 8:2–8:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev8:26\">LEV 8:26</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev10:12\">LEV 10:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num6:14-Num6:15\">NUM 6:14–6:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num6:19\">NUM 6:19</a></p>\n<h2>Some offerings contained yeast</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev23:17\">LEV 23:17</a></strong></p>\n<h2>Yeast as an image of the kingdom of God</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt13:33\">MAT 13:33</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke13:20-Luke13:21\">LUK 13:20–13:21</a></p>\n<h2>Metaphorical references to yeast as something evil</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor5:6-1Cor5:8\">1CO 5:6–5:8</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt16:5-Matt16:12\">MAT 16:5–16:12</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark8:14-Mark8:21\">MRK 8:14–8:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke12:1-Luke12:3\">LUK 12:1–12:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal5:2-Gal5:12\">GAL 5:2–5:12</a></p>",
